OL,3,CHow Clare's Law can help prevent
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse in Jersey
OL,6,FThe States of Jersey Police is
OL,7,Fpromoting The Clare's Law campaign to
OL,8,Fbetter protect islanders from domestic
OL,9,Fabusers.
OL,11,FThe Domestic Abuse Disclosure Scheme
OL,12,Fenables the police to inform
OL,13,Findividuals who may feel at risk of
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse about their partner's
OL,15,Fhistory of abusive behaviour.
OL,17,FThe campaign was a recommendation in
OL,18,Fthe Violence Against Women and Girls
OL,19,Ftaskforce report in November 2023.
OL,21,FClare's Law has two elements:
