OL,3,CHow Clare's Law can help prevent
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse in Jersey
OL,6,F"Clare's Law has been around since
OL,7,F2014, however, the public in Jersey
OL,8,Freally has not taken up on their
OL,9,F'right to ask', and I think that is
OL,10,Fbecause it is not well publicised
OL,11,Fenough so hence why we have set up
OL,12,Fthis campaign nearly 10 years later."
OL,14,FShe adds: "Police often hold multiple
OL,15,Freports of abuse from different
OL,16,Fvictims of the same perpetrator.
OL,17,FSerial abusers don't stop and Clare's
OL,18,FLaw can reveal and disrupt these
OL,19,Fperpetrators."
