OL,3,CHow Clare's Law can help prevent
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse in Jersey
OL,6,FA woman who was attacked and raped by
OL,7,Fformer Jersey restaurant owner Gavin
OL,8,FNeil Roberts used the Clare's Law
OL,9,Fscheme and used her voice to
OL,10,Fdemonstrate to others to come forward
OL,11,Fand be heard.
OL,13,FIn Jersey, domestic abuse accounts for
OL,14,F15% of crime.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Craig
OL,17,FJackson says: "We are making more and
OL,18,Fmore disclosures every year but we
OL,19,Fwould encourage everyone to make
OL,20,Fbetter use of Clare's Law to prevent
OL,21,Fdomestic abuse."
